        <div class="two-third individual-content">
            <h2>Meet Trayvonta</h2>
            <h4>Born July 2001</h4>
            <p>Trayvonta has a creative and artistic talent; he loves to design jewelry and clothes. He dreams of being a designer and visiting Hollywood when he is grown. He enjoys reading chapter books, listening to Motown artists like the Jackson 5 and enjoys going to the movies especially the Tyler Perry series of <i>Madea</i> films. Comedies on television and in the theaters are his favorite because he loves to laugh.<a href="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/trayvonta1.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3651 " src="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/trayvonta1.jpg" alt="" width="456" height="684" /></a></p>
<p>Trayvonta is an intelligent young man who enjoys school. His favorite subject is math and he excels in his studies achieving As and Bs in all his classes. When not in school, Trayvonta likes to spend time playing Monopoly, going to movies and shopping. In the summer months, he enjoys playing basketball, trips to Kings Island and camping.</p>
<p>Trayvonta is very helpful around the house by cleaning his room, bathroom and taking out the garbage. He helps wherever he can. He is a kind, respectful, courteous teen with a dynamic personality.</p>
<p>He is looking for a loving family to help him grow and achieve his dreams.</p>

